OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FThe world's first mobile cancer care
OL,7,Funit has been refurbished to make
OL,8,Ftreatment more accessible for patients
OL,9,Fin Gloucestershire and relieve
OL,10,Fpressure from hospitals.
OL,12,FThe mobile care unit, named Helen, is
OL,13,Fintended to come closer to patients
OL,14,Fwho are in need of life-saving care.
OL,16,FThe unit was built in Yate and
OL,17,Fprovided by the cancer care charity
OL,18,FHope for Tomorrow in partnership with
OL,19,FGloucestershire Hospitals NHS
OL,20,FFoundation Trust.
