OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FHelen originally launched in 2007 as
OL,7,Fthe world's first mobile cancer care
OL,8,Funit, and has been replaced with a
OL,9,Fnewly upgraded unit.
OL,11,F'It's easy access for me' - patient
OL,13,FGeoff Small is getting his
OL,14,Fchemotherapy in the mobile clinic
OL,15,Fparked at Stroud hospital.
OL,17,FThe oncology unit Cheltenham, which is
OL,18,Fthe centre for cancer treatment in the
OL,19,FGloucestershire, would take an hour
OL,20,Ffor him to get there and back.
