OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FBut now he's able to get treated much
OL,7,Fcloser to home, it's easier and less
OL,8,Ftiring. Geoff told ITV West Country
OL,9,Fhow the new unit is making him receive
OL,10,Fcare more efficiently
OL,12,FHe said: "It's easy access for me.
OL,13,FNice and comfortable. I should be
OL,14,Fgetting my coffee and biscuits in a
OL,15,Fminute.
OL,17,F"It all the costs and time, and
OL,18,Fthere's not always a parking space
OL,19,Favailable at Cheltenham (hospital), so
OL,20,Fit's a bit of a problem if you can't
OL,21,Fpark."
