OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,F'It's more comfortable for the
OL,7,Fpatient' - staff
OL,9,FThe scheme was launched back in 2007
OL,10,Fin the county by the late former
OL,11,Fracing driver Sir Stirling Moss.
OL,13,FIt was revolutionary back then and was
OL,14,Fthe first mobile chemotherapy clinic
OL,15,Fof its kind in the world.
OL,17,FFor patients who don't have their own
OL,18,Ftransport, it has proved invaluable.
