OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FAlmost a third of patients save over
OL,7,Fthree hours in travel, waiting, and
OL,8,Ftreatment time per visit.
OL,10,FStaff at the cancer clinic said: "It's
OL,11,Fthe fact that the patients are having
OL,12,Fsuch a much better experience, even
OL,13,Fthough they are still going to have
OL,14,Fall the unpleasant side effects of
OL,15,Fcancer treatment."
OL,17,FThe mobile clinics cost around
OL,18,F#300,000 pounds and are provided by
OL,19,Fthe charity Hope for Tomorrow.
