OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FThey have a lifespan of about 10 years
OL,7,Fbefore they are either replaced or
OL,8,Fgiven an upgrade - like Helen.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for charity Hope for
OL,11,FTomorrow said: "It's more comfortable
OL,12,Ffor the patient.
OL,14,F"It might have a bit more space. It's
OL,15,Fclean, it's comfortable, it's
OL,16,Faccessible.
OL,18,F"And it goes out to locations in
OL,19,FGloucestershire every day, a different
OL,20,Fplace, bringing cancer care closer to
OL,21,Fthe patients that need it."
