OL,3,CWorld's first mobile cancer care unit
OL,4,Ctransforms patients' lives
OL,6,FTina Seymour, Chief Executive of Hope
OL,7,Ffor Tomorrow, said: "It's vital that
OL,8,Fwe keep our mobile units in the best
OL,9,Fpossible condition to support both
OL,10,Fpatients and the incredible NHS teams
OL,11,Fwho provide the best care on board.
OL,13,F"We are so grateful to everyone who
OL,14,Fhas supported our fundraising efforts
OL,15,F` it's thanks to their generosity that
OL,16,Fwe've been able to make this upgrade
OL,17,Fpossible."
